Package fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.datastore.store

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PersistentStore
    This interface extends the InternalEObject.EStore interface and allows to establish a mapping between Resources and InternalEObject.EStores.
    TransientStore  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDirectWriteStore<P extends PersistenceBackend>  
    AbstractPersistentStore  
    AbstractPersistentStoreDecorator
    A PersistentStore wrapper that delegates method calls to an internal PersistentStore.
    AbstractTransientStore
    A simple InternalEObject.EStore implementation that uses collections to store the data in memory.
    AutocommitStoreDecorator  
    FeatureCachingStoreDecorator
    A PersistentStore decorator that caches EStructuralFeature.
    InvalidStore
    Utility class which can be used by backend-specific implementations that does not provide a transient layer.
    IsSetCachingStoreDecorator
    A PersistentStore wrapper that caches the presence of a value.
    LoadedObjectCounterStoreDecorator  
    LoggingStoreDecorator
    A PersistentStore decorator that logs every call to its methods in the NeoLogger.
    OwnedTransientStore
    A AbstractTransientStore that belongs to a single EObject owner.
    SizeCachingStoreDecorator
    A PersistentStore decorator that caches the size data.
    SynchronizedTransientStore
    A simple InternalEObject.EStore implementation that uses synchronized collections to store the data in memory, using Collections.synchronizedMap(java.util.Map).
